Ranger Help for: trailmark
===========================

SYNTAX:      trailmark <message>
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     15
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to leave a trail marker in the current room
with a short message attached. Only other Rangers can see trail markers.
These markers are useful for leaving directions, warnings, or notes for
fellow Rangers who pass through the area. Trail markers persist for a
limited time before fading. Use 'signs' or 'trailsigns' to read any
markers left in the current room.
